@startuml seq-06-profile-update
title PATCH /auth/profile

actor "User" as U <<human>>
participant "Browser" as B <<browser>>
participant "Express\n+ authenticateToken" as API <<service>>
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

B -> API: PATCH /auth/profile\nBearer + JSON body (optional fields)

API -> API: Zod patchProfileBody
alt No fields / invalid avatar URL rule
  API --> B: 400
else OK
  API -> DB: prisma.user.update\n(merge fields; if email changed:\n authVersion++)
  alt Unique constraint (email / badge)
    API --> B: 409 conflict
  else Success
    opt emailChanged
      API -> DB: revoke all refresh sessions
      API -> API: issueSessionTokens + setRefreshCookie
    end
    API -> API: mapUserResponse + manager fields
    API --> B: 200 { user, token? }
  end
end

note right of API
  Source: **apps/api/src/routes/auth.ts** (~546+),
  **isAllowedProfilePictureUrlForUser**.
end note

@enduml
